---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Text Diff Checker
description: Free online text diff checker. Compare two texts side by side and see differences highlighted. Find additions, deletions, and modifications instantly.
keywords: diff checker, text compare, text diff, compare text online, difference checker, file compare, code diff
permalink: /tools/diff-checker/
toolId: diff-checker
toolJs: diff-checker.js
ogImage: diff-checker.jpg
---
{# Get tool data from tools.json #}
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<!-- Schema.org BreadcrumbList -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Tools", "item": "{{ site.url }}/#tools"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "{{ toolData.name }}", "item": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}"}
  ]
}
</script>

<!-- Schema.org WebApplication -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "{{ toolData.fullName }}",
  "description": "{{ description }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}",
  "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any",
  "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript",
  "offers": {"@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD"},
  "author": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}"}
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
  .diff-inputs { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .diff-inputs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .diff-input-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .diff-input-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .diff-textarea { min-height: 200px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); resize: vertical; }
  .diff-stats { display: flex; gap: var(--space-6); padding: var(--space-4); background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: var(--radius-md); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .diff-stat { text-align: center; }
  .diff-stat-value { font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: 600; }
  .diff-stat-value.additions { color: #16a34a; }
  .diff-stat-value.deletions { color: #dc2626; }
  .diff-stat-value.unchanged { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .diff-stat-label { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-muted); }
  .diff-output { margin-top: var(--space-4); }
  .diff-view-toggle { display: flex; gap: var(--space-2); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
  .diff-result { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.6; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; }
  .diff-line { display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .diff-line:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .diff-line-number { min-width: 40px; padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2); background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--text-muted); text-align: right; font-size: var(--text-xs); border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border); user-select: none; }
  .diff-line-content { flex: 1; padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; }
  .diff-line.addition { background: #dcfce7; }
  .diff-line.addition .diff-line-content { color: #166534; }
  .diff-line.deletion { background: #fee2e2; }
  .diff-line.deletion .diff-line-content { color: #991b1b; }
  .diff-line.modification { background: #fef9c3; }
  .diff-line.modification .diff-line-content { color: #854d0e; }
  .diff-char-add { background: #86efac; padding: 0 1px; border-radius: 2px; }
  .diff-char-del { background: #fca5a5; padding: 0 1px; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: line-through; }
  .diff-side-by-side { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .diff-side { overflow-x: auto; }
  .diff-side-header { padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: var(--color-bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
  .diff-empty { padding: var(--space-8); text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<div class="tool-container">
  <!-- Input Section -->
  <div class="diff-inputs">
    <div class="diff-input-group">
      <div class="diff-input-header">
        <label for="text-original" class="input-label">Original Text</label>
        <button type="button" id="sample-diff" class="btn btn-text btn-sm">Load Sample</button>
      </div>
      <textarea id="text-original" class="tool-textarea diff-textarea" placeholder="Paste original text here..." spellcheck="false"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-input-group">
      <div class="diff-input-header">
        <label for="text-modified" class="input-label">Modified Text</label>
        <button type="button" id="swap-texts" class="btn btn-text btn-sm">Swap</button>
      </div>
      <textarea id="text-modified" class="tool-textarea diff-textarea" placeholder="Paste modified text here..." spellcheck="false"></textarea>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Action Buttons -->
  <div class="tool-actions">
    <button type="button" id="compare-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Compare</button>
    <button type="button" id="clear-diff" class="btn btn-ghost">Clear All</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="diff-stats" id="diff-stats">
    <div class="diff-stat">
      <div class="diff-stat-value additions" id="stat-additions">0</div>
      <div class="diff-stat-label">Additions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-stat">
      <div class="diff-stat-value deletions" id="stat-deletions">0</div>
      <div class="diff-stat-label">Deletions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-stat">
      <div class="diff-stat-value unchanged" id="stat-unchanged">0</div>
      <div class="diff-stat-label">Unchanged</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Output Section -->
  <div class="diff-output">
    <div class="diff-view-toggle">
      <button type="button" class="btn-option diff-view-btn active" data-view="unified">Unified</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn-option diff-view-btn" data-view="split">Side by Side</button>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-result" id="diff-result">
      <div class="diff-empty">Enter text in both fields and click Compare to see differences.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- How to Use Section -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>How to Use</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">1</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Paste Original</h3><p>Enter or paste your original text in the left text area.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">2</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Paste Modified</h3><p>Enter or paste the modified version in the right text area.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">3</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Compare</h3><p>Click "Compare" to see the differences highlighted.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">4</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Review Changes</h3><p>Green shows additions, red shows deletions. Toggle between unified and side-by-side views.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">What algorithm is used for diff?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>This tool uses a line-by-line diff algorithm similar to the Unix diff command. It identifies additions, deletions, and unchanged lines between the two texts.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">What do the colors mean?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p><strong>Green</strong> indicates lines added in the modified text. <strong>Red</strong> indicates lines deleted from the original. <strong>White/unchanged</strong> lines appear in both texts.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">What's the difference between unified and side-by-side view?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p><strong>Unified</strong> shows all changes in a single column with +/- prefixes. <strong>Side by side</strong> shows original and modified texts in parallel columns for easier comparison.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Is there a size limit?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>The tool works best with texts up to 10,000 lines. Larger texts may be slower to process. All processing happens in your browser.</p></div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Related Tools -->
<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Related Tools</h2>
  <div class="related-tools">
    {% for tool in tools %}
    {% if tool.id != toolId %}
    <a href="/tools/{{ tool.id }}/" class="related-tool-link">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" width="16" height="16">{{ tool.icon | safe }}</svg>
      {{ tool.name }}
    </a>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
